race.comment: DELRICO (2) looks well placed here on recent form in richer company. Fourth in a hot form race here two back then a close-up seventh on the Gold Coast last time when had the thumps. Change of rider and best figures stack right up. Goes close. CELESTIAL BLAZE (1) is racing very well and is long overdue. Led and grabbed right on the line last three, the latest over 2200m at Eagle Farm. Goes well here and despite more weight will take running down. HEROIC REBEL (3) raced on speed with Moor aboard and cleared out for a big maiden win. First try at the trip but hard fit and back in form and will give a sight again. USE YOUR ILLUSION (5) is another overdue for a win. Placed last two but does have a good record here and should be winding up strongly. ARGERICH (11) is still a maiden but has upside. Has a nice weight and can give a sight on speed.
